title: Miele Pro-Style Induction Range HR1622I Overview
description:
Miele 30  Pro-Style Stainless Steel Induction Range - HR1622 I - http://abt.com/product/87561/Miele-HR1622I.html

Features:
• M Touch controls and backlit knobs
• EasyClean Ceran surface with 4 variable cooking zones 
• Booster function
• TwinPower Convection fans 
• 21 Operating modes including Self-Clean 
• Moisture Plus 
• MasterChef and MasterChef Plus automatic programs 
• Wireless Roast Probe 
• Soft Close and Soft Open 
• Clean Touch Steel™ front
